  <description type="morphology">Leaf blades (proximal) 5–35 cm × 4–15 mm. Phyllaries 7–14 mm. Disc corollas 5–8 mm. Ray cypselae 5–7 mm; pappi 0 or to 0.7 mm. Disc cypselae 5–9 mm; pappi 1–5 mm. 2n = 12.</description>
